**BitTrust** is a website that offers reviews for online merchants that accept bitcoin. The site aims to solve the problem of non-trustworthy bitcoin-related services.

## Reviews
Services and merchants can have their websites reviewed by BitTrust by submitting them to the site. BitTrust claims to evaluate submitted listings within 24 hours of submission. Users can also submit reviews for services that they have used.

Sites are listed on BitTrust through a categorization system.
